using python command create virtual enviroment
$python -m venv myenv(folder name)
for activate this 
-- in side folder we have scripts and a activate file and we need to excecute this file
$ myenv/Secripts/activate
now my virtual enviroment is active 
by default this use verson of python
#deactivate (command for deactivate virtul enviroment)

--------------------
$ pip install virtualenv
$ virtual -p python3 virtual_env_name
$virtualenv_name\scripts\activate
$deactivate

----------------------
by using conda create
$conda create -p venv1 python==3.12 -y
$conda activate venv1
$ conda deactivate

